sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Brand } from '../brand'; import { BrandService } from '../services/brand/brand.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-backend-requests', templateUrl: './backend-requests.component.html', styleUrls: ['./backend-requests.component.css'] }) export class BackendRequestsComponent { constructor(private heroService: BrandService) { } getBrands(){ return this.heroService.getBrands(); } }
